  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ὁ</span>  <span data-text=\"δᾶμος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">δᾶμος</span>  <span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">τῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἐγεσταίων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">Ἐγεσταίων</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάλακρον\n                    Διοδώρου Ἐρύσσιον\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάλακρον\"><span data-text=\"Φάλακρον\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">Φάλα[κρον]</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-text=\"Διοδώρου\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">[Δ]ιοδώ̣ρου</span></span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ἐρύσσιον\"><span data-text=\"Ἐρύσσιον\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">Ἐρύσσιον</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἀρετᾶς\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">ἀρετᾶς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἕνεκα\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">ἕνε[κα]</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"δᾶμος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΔΑΜΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Ἐγεσταίων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΓΕΣΤΑΙΩΝ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φάλακρον\n                    Διοδώρου Ἐρύσσιον\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φάλακρον\"><span data-text=\"Φάλακρον\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">ΦΑΛΑ[....]</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-text=\"Διοδώρου\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">[.]ΙΟΔ.ΡΟΥ</span></span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ἐρύσσιον\"><span data-text=\"Ἐρύσσιον\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΡΥΣΣΙΟΝ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἀρετᾶς\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">ΑΡΕΤΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἕνεκα\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">ΕΝΕ[..]</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001107_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2022-05-23; courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic001107_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001107.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2022-05-23; courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic001107-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Ampolo and Erdas 2019</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>The people of the Segestans (honours/dedicates) Phalakros Eyrssios, son of Diodoros, on account of his virtue.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a class=\"translation-source\" href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></